---
import DocsLayout from '../../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
const title = 'Streaming';
---

<DocsLayout title={title}>
<h1>Streaming</h1>
<p>Stream responses as Server-Sent Events (SSE) by setting <code>stream: true</code>. Each chunk is delivered as a <code>data:</code> line, allowing real-time display of generated text.</p>
<pre><code>{`curl --no-buffer -X POST http://localhost:18645/v1/responses \
  -H 'Authorization: Bearer anything' \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  -d '{
  "model": "grok-4.3",
  "stream": true,
  "input": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Write a haiku about streaming."}
  ]
}'`}</code></pre>
</DocsLayout>
